  "architecture_summary": "Swin Transformer is a hierarchical vision Transformer that computes self-attention within non-overlapping local windows and alternates with shifted window partitioning to enable cross-window connections. It builds multi-scale feature maps through patch merging, giving linear computational complexity with respect to image size and making it suitable as a general-purpose backbone for vision tasks.",
